COHERENCE & STABILITY

Local Drift:
φ_i(t+1) = φ_i(t) + ε

Coherence Decay:
C(r) = exp(-λ r)

Errors remain local, not global.

PHASE OS INTEGRATION

Phase OS schedules:

local update windows

